The reported information relates to assets underlying the reported information that have an investment capital factor of 0.5% as determined in accordance relevant prudential standards.
These items are: - debt obligations of the Commonwealth Government, an Australian State or Territory government, or the national government of a foreign country where the security has a Grade 1 counterparty rating or, if not rated, the long-term, foreign currency counterparty rating of that country is Grade 1;
- Assets in respect of anticipated recoveries from the Commonwealth Government or from an Australian State or Territory government.
